<emphasis id="579E2338FFFCFFC3FF71FF44FE86FF1F" bold="true" box="[151,379,150,177]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Eudocima tyrannus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="017B82DBFFFCFFC3FE6CFF44FDD3FF1E" author="Guenee, A. M." box="[394,558,150,177]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" refId="ref37734" refString="Guenee, A. M. (1852) Histoire naturelle des Insectes. VII. Species general des Lepidopteres. Noctuelites. Tome III. Librairie Encyclopedique de Roret, Paris, 442 pp." type="book" year="1852">Guenée, 1852</bibRefCitation>
